hopobject.body: I've just graduated pharmacy price disclosure However, the merged company will be led by an American CEOafter a 30 month transition and overseen from a headquarters onneutral ground in the Netherlands - far from the Paris home ofPublicis near the Arc de Triomphe. Maurice Levy, the veteran CEOof Publicis whose French-accented English is a reminder of theagency's roots, will take the less visible role of non-executivechairman.
